import React from 'react'
import ReactDOM from 'react-dom'
import { BrowserRouter } from "react-router-dom";
import './index.css'
import App from './App'
import * as serviceWorker from './serviceWorker'


ReactDOM.render(
    <BrowserRouter>
      <App />
    </BrowserRouter>,
  document.getElementById("root")
)

serviceWorker.unregister()
